divs: Sighting Details1.Was at residence walking back from dumpster.2.Yellow object in clear night sky.3.Trianglar yellow object traveling across sky in level soundless flight.4.Trianglar yellow object with three small orbs attached via tublinks emmitting yellow steady light travelling from sw to ne direction apprx 500 ft agl. Steady level soundless flight.5.Was attempting to identify object and keep it in view as long as possible.After sighting,called Marquette City Police Dept and reported it..Event#1309060055.6.Object continued on steady ne path until out of sight.
